quran[24{c,v,t}:
37,103,Falammaaa aslamaa wa tallahoo liljabeen
37,104,Wa naadainaahu ai yaaaa Ibraheem
37,105,Qad saddaqtar ru'yaa; innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
37,106,Inna haazaa lahuwal balaaa'ul mubeen
37,107,Wa fadainaahu bizibhin 'azeem
37,108,Wa taraknaa 'alaihi fil aakhireen
37,109,Salaamun 'alaaa Ibraaheem
37,110,Kazaalika najzil muhsineen
37,111,Innahoo min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
37,112,Wa bashsharnaahu bi Ishaaqa Nabiyayam minas saaliheen
37,113,Wa baaraknaa 'alaihi wa 'alaaa Ishaaq; wa min zurriyya tihimaa muhsinunw wa zaalimul linafshihee mubeen�(section 3)
37,114,Wa laqad mananna alaa Moosaa wa Haaroon
37,115,Wa najjainaahumaa wa qawmahumaa minal karbil 'azeem
37,116,Wa nasarnaahum fakaanoo humul ghaalibeen
37,117,Wa aatainaahumal Kitaabal mustabeen
37,118,Wa hadainaahumus Siraatal Mustaqeem
37,119,Wa taraknaa 'alaihimaa fil aakhireen
37,120,Salaamun 'alaa Moosaa wa Haaroon
37,121,Innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
37,122,Innahumaa min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
37,123,Wa inna Ilyaasa laminal mursaleen
37,124,Iz qaala liqawmiheee alaa tattaqoon
37,125,Atad'oona Ba'lanw wa tazaroona ahsanal khaaliqeen
37,126,Allaaha Rabbakum wa Rabba aabaaa'ikumul awwaleen
